te mandatory? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Is the Care Certificate mandatory? - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-23_"/></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-9298" data-category="Generic Content" data-name="Matcha" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-dBFCZX khzvmY pf-24_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-gvPcJq dRaLso"><div class="sc-hzhKNl fltMam pf-25_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:0px;--s-sm:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fatbYi lnCFtg pf-26_"><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-27_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-29_">The Care Certificate is an accreditation that is often required for new healthcare support workers and adult social care workers entering the sector. In this blog, we will explore whether the <a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/care-certificate-train-the-trainer-trainer-pack-cpduk-accredited?variant=31839814582341" target="_blank"><i><span style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204);">Care Certificate</span></i></a> is mandatory or not.</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-30_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-32_">Is it mandatory to obtain the Care Certificate?</span></h2><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Is_it_mandatory_to_obtain_the_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_e551e569-0883-4100-a4eb-5a559708d2ac.jpg?v=1693911257" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Is_it_mandatory_to_obtain_the_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_e551e569-0883-4100-a4eb-5a559708d2ac.jpg?v=1693911257 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Is_it_mandatory_to_obtain_the_Care_Certificate_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK_e551e569-0883-4100-a4eb-5a559708d2ac_500x.jpg?v=1693911257 320w" width="2000" height="1304" alt="Is it mandatory to obtain the Care Certificate - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" title="Is it mandatory to obtain the Care Certificate - The Mandatory Training Group UK -" data-pf-type="Image3" class="sc-gtJxSR jkHSry pf-33_"/><p class="sc-eONOlN cfGtgs pf-34_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-36_">In a nutshell no, the Care Certificate is not universally mandatory for all healthcare professionals. Unlike certain certifications or licenses that are legally required to practice in specific fields, there is no obligation for all healthcare workers to hold a Care Certificate.<br><br>However, it is important to note that while it may not be mandatory in a legal sense, the Care Quality Commission (CQC) expects appropriate staff who are new to the services they regulate to achieve the competencies required by the Care Certificate as part of their induction. The CQC has the power to enforce regulations related to staff training and will ensure that providers have staff inductions and training that meet the same standards as the Care Certificate if they choose not to use it. Furthermore, the CQC’s guidance for providers includes references to the Care Certificate under CQC’s Regulation 18 on Staffing and Regulation 19 on fit and proper persons employed.<br> </span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-fUklNj thmnJ pf-37_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-cHMHbD bwTmDt pf-39_">Benefits of obtaining the Care Certificate </span></h3><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Benefits_of_obtaining_the_Care_Certificate_-_Online_training_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693911357" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Benefits_of_obtaining_the_Care_Certificate_-_Online_training_-_The_Mandatory_Training_Group_UK.jpg?v=1693911357 1536w, https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0937/2788/files/Benefits_of_obtaining_the_Care_Certificate_-_Online_training_-_The_Mandatory_Trainin